    public static enum ConnectIQ.IQMessageStatus

    Enumeration returned from sendMessage() or provided when a message is received from a Connect IQ device.
    Since:
    1.0

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FAILURE_DURING_TRANSFER
      An error occurred when transferring the message to the device.
      FAILURE_INVALID_DEVICE
      A request was made to send data to an invalid device.
      FAILURE_INVALID_FORMAT
      A message being sent or received was not in a valid Monkey C format.
      FAILURE_MESSAGE_TOO_LARGE
      A message being sent when serialized is too long.
      FAILURE_UNKNOWN
      An unknown error occurred during the send or receive of a message.
      FAILURE_UNSUPPORTED_TYPE
      A data type passed to sendMessage() is not a valid data type that can be serialized to a Monkey C format.
      SUCCESS
      Message was sent/received successfully.
